                        <interp inst="t18431127-name-730" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES PRING</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No.</hi> 128.) I was on duty—the pri<lb></lb>soner came and told me his master's name—he said he had received the money, and had spent or made away with it; he had done wrong, and asked whether I would take him, or whether he should go to the inspector—I took him to the station.</p>
